headline: U.S. Bank Named Official Banking and Wealth Management Partner of Premier Lacrosse League and Women’s Lacrosse League
summary: NEW YORK, May 27, 2025--The Premier Lacrosse League (PLL) and Women's Lacrosse League (WLL) announced today a multi-year partnership with U.S. Bank, establishing it as the Official Banking and Wealth Management Partner of both leagues. The partnership, which begins with the 2025 season launching May 30, represents a strategic investment in the growth of professional lacrosse.
